{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "Faktoora e-Invoicing API",
    "description": "# About the e-Invoicing API\n\nThe Faktoora e-Invoicing API provides services to create and manage electronic invoices in compliance with European standard EN16931. It supports generating XRechnung, ZUGFeRD (PDF/A3), and simple PDF invoices.\n\n## Features\n- Create structured electronic invoices.\n- Import and validate incoming invoices in supported formats.\n- Receive notifications via webhooks upon invoice generation completion.\n\n## Sending Invoices\n- The API provides the option to send invoices directly to the recipient upon creation. This functionality can be configured in the `delivery` section of the payload.\n- Invoices can be sent via an external SMTP server. To enable this, the SMTP server details must be configured in the Faktoora account settings. This feature allows greater flexibility in managing outgoing email communications.\n\n## Invoice Creation Pattern\n- Invoice creation in the Faktoora API is **asynchronous**. This means that when an invoice creation request is submitted, the process does not complete immediately.\n- Upon successful submission of the request, the API responds with a **202 Accepted** status and provides a unique `faktooraId` for the invoice creation task.\n- The `faktooraId` can be used to retrieve the generated invoice once the creation process is complete. There are two main approaches for this:\n  1. **Polling**: The client can periodically make GET requests to fetch the invoice using the `faktooraId`.\n  2. **Webhook Notification**: A webhook can be registered to receive real-time notifications when the invoice is ready. The webhook will include the `faktooraId` and other relevant details.\n- This pattern ensures scalability and reliability by allowing the API to handle invoice creation tasks asynchronously, even under high loads.\n",
    "version": "1.0",
    "x-jentic-source-url": "https://api.faktoora.com/api/v1/api-docs"
  },
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "Invoices",
      "description": "Endpoints for managing and retrieving invoices."
    },
    {
      "name": "Invoice import",
      "description": "Endpoints for importing and validating invoices."
    },
    {
      "name": "Incoming Import Invoice",
      "description": "Endpoints for importing and validating incoming invoices."
    },
    {
      "name": "Outgoing Import Invoice",
      "description": "Endpoints for importing and validating outgoing invoices."
    },
    {
      "name": "Webhooks",
      "description": "Endpoints for managing webhook subscriptions."
    },
    {
      "name": "Products",
      "description": "Endpoints for managing products."
    },
    {
      "name": "Product Bundles",
      "description": "Endpoints for managing product bundles."
    },
    {
      "name": "Customers",
      "description": "Endpoints for managing customers."
    }
  ],
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "https://api.faktoora.com/api/v1",
      "description": "Production Instance"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://api.demo.faktoora.com/api/v1",
      "description": "Demo Instance"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/invoices": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "Invoices"
        ],
        "summary": "Create an electronic invoice",
        "description": "This endpoint creates an electronic invoice from structured data. It supports generating ZUGFeRD (PDF/A3 with embedded XML) or XRechnung (XML-only).\nWebhooks can be used to receive notifications upon completion of the invoice generation process.\n",
        "security": [
          {
            "apiKeyAuth": []
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "invoices": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                      "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Invoice"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "202": {
            "description": "Invoice creation request accepted and processing started.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                      "faktooraId": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Unique identifier for the created invoice.",
                        "example": "INV123456"
                      },
                      "detailsPage": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "URL to view the invoice details.",
                        "example": "https://faktoora.com/invoice/details/a81bc81b-dead-4e5d-abff-90865d1e13b1"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Invalid request payload.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Unauthorized request."
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "Internal server error occurred.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ValidationError"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "operationId": "postInvoices"
      },
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Invoices"
        ],
        "summary": "List all current invoices",
        "description": "Returns a paginated list of all current invoices with filtering, sorting, and search capabilities.\n",
        "security": [
          {
            "apiKeyAuth": []
          }
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "page",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "minimum": 1,
              "default": 1
            },
            "description": "Page number for pagination"
          },
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "perPage",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "minimum": 1,
              "maximum": 100,
              "default": 10
            },
            "description": "Number of items per page"
          },
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "sort",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": [
                "faktooraId",
                "invoiceNumber",
                "issueDate",
                "createdAt"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Field to sort by"
          },
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "order",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": [
                "asc",
                "desc"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Sort order"
          },
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "keyword",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "description": "Search keyword for filtering invoices"
          },
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "invoiceNumber",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "description": "Filter by invoiceNumber"
          },
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "startIssueDate",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "date-time"
            },
            "description": "Filter by issue date range start"
          },
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "endIssueDate",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "date-time"
            },
            "description": "Filter by issue date range end"
          },
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "startDate",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "date-time"
            },
            "description": "Filter by creation date range start"
          },
          {
            "in": "query",
            "name": "endDate",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "date-time"
            },
            "description": "Filter by creation date range end"
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Paginated list of all current invoices",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "data": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "items": {
                        "$ref": "#/components/schemas/InvoiceItemDto"
                      }
                    },
                    "meta": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "page": {
                          "type": "integer",
                          "description": "Current page number"
                        },
                        "perPage": {
                          "type": "integer",
                          "description": "Items per page"
                        },
                        "totalPages": {
                          "type": "integer",
                          "description": "Total number of pages"
                        },
                        "totalItems": {
                          "type": "integer",
                          "description": "Total number of items"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Invalid request parameters",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Unauthorized request"
          }
        },
        "operationId": "getInvoices"
      }
    },
    "/invoices/{faktooraId}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Invoices"
        ],
        "summary": "Retrieve an invoice by Faktoora ID",
        "description": "Download an invoice using its Faktoora ID, which is returned after invoice creation. The response contains the invoice in either PDF or XML format.\n",
        "security": [
          {
            "apiKeyAuth": []
          }
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "in": "path",
            "name": "faktooraId",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "description": "Faktoora ID of the invoice."
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "The requested invoice in PDF or XML format.",
            "content": {
              "application/pdf": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "format": "binary"
                }
              },
              "application/xml": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "format": "binary"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Invalid request payload.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Unauthorized request."
          },
          "404": {
            "description": "Invoice not found.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "operationId": "getInvoicesByFaktooraid"
      },
      "delete": {
        "summary": "Delete a specific invoice by faktooraId",
        "description": "Delete an invoice referenced via faktooraId. `invoiceDeleteMode` must be enabled in order to do this action.",
        "tags": [
          "Invoices"
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "type": "string",
            "required": true,
            "in": "path",
            "name": "faktooraId"
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Default Response"
          }
        },
        "operationId": "deleteInvoicesByFaktooraid"
      }
    },
    "/invoices/{faktooraId}/status": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Invoices"
        ],
        "summary": "Get invoice post-processing status",
        "description": "Returns the current status of invoice processing including authority registration, delivery information, and job completion status. \nThis endpoint is designed for checking status tracking after invoice creation.\n\n**Authority Registration:**\n- Returns an array of authority registration details if `authorityRegistration` is configured on the invoice\n- Currently supports Verifactu authority type with invoice type and correction mode\n- Returns empty array if no authority registration is configured\n\n**Delivery Information:**\n- Returns delivery attempts from the `deliveryData` field\n- For email deliveries: includes recipient, carbonCopy, and blindCarbonCopy fields\n- For manual deliveries: only includes the type field\n- Multiple delivery attempts may be present in the array\n- Returns empty array if no delivery has been attempted\n\n**Job Status:**\n- Returns \"done\" when invoice file generation is complete\n- For `simple` profile: checks only if PDF file exists\n- For other profiles (xrechnung, zugferd, etc.): checks if both PDF and XML files exist\n- Returns undefined (not included in response) if files are not yet generated\n",
        "security": [
          {
            "apiKeyAuth": []
          }
        ],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "in": "path",
            "name": "faktooraId",
            "required": true,
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "description": "Faktoora ID of the invoice."
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Invoice status retrieved successfully",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "required": [
                    "authority",
                    "delivery",
                    "invoiceStatus"
                  ],
                  "properties": {
                    "authority": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "description": "Array of authority registration entries. Empty if no authority registration is configured.\n",
                      "items": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "required": [
                          "type"
                        ],
                        "properties": {
                          "type": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "enum": [
                              "verifactu"
                            ],
                            "description": "Type of authority registration",
                            "example": "verifactu"
                          },
                          "verifactuType": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "Verifactu invoice type (F1-F4 or R1-R5)",
                            "example": "R1"
                          },
                          "verifactuCorrectionMode": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "Correction mode for Verifactu. Only present when verifactuType is R1, R2, R3, R4, or R5.\n",
                            "example": "I"
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "delivery": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "description": "Array of delivery attempts. Empty if invoice has not been delivered yet.\n",
                      "items": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "required": [
                          "type"
                        ],
                        "properties": {
                          "type": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "Type of delivery method",
                            "enum": [
                              "email",
                              "manual"
                            ],
                            "example": "email"
                          },
                          "recipient": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "format": "email",
                            "description": "Primary recipient email address. Only present when type is \"email\".\n",
                            "example": "check@email.com"
                          },
                          "carbonCopy": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "Comma-separated list of CC recipients. Only present when type is \"email\" and CC addresses exist.\n",
                            "example": "cc1@gmail.com, cc2@gmail.com"
                          },
                          "blindCarbonCopy": {
                            "type": "string",
                            "description": "Comma-separated list of BCC recipients. Only present when type is \"email\" and BCC addresses exist.\n",
                            "example": "bcc@gmail.com"
                          }
                        }
                      }
                    },
                    "jobStatus": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "enum": [
                        "done"
                      ],
                      "description": "File generation status. Returns \"done\" when invoice files are ready for download.\n- For `simple` profile: PDF file must be generated\n- For other profiles: Both PDF and XML files must be generated\n\nThis field is omitted from the response if files are not yet ready.\n",
                      "example": "done"
                    },
                    "invoiceStatus": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Current processing status of the invoice",
                      "example": "created"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Invalid request payload.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Unauthorized request"
          },
          "404": {
            "description": "Invoice not found",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "operationId": "getInvoicesByFaktooraidStatus"
      }
    },
    "/import": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "Invoice import"
        ],
        "summary": "Import an e-invoice",
        "description": "Upload an e-invoice in XRechnung or ZUGFeRD format for validation and processing.\n",
        "security": [
          {
            "apiKeyAuth": []
          }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "multipart/form-data": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "file": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "format": "binary",
                    "description": "The invoice file to be uploaded."
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "202": {
            "description": "Invoice upload accepted for processing.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "importId": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "Unique identifier for the import task.",
                      "example": "IMP456789"
                    },
                    "detailsPage": {
                      "type": "string",
                      "description": "URL to view the import task details.",
                      "example": "https://faktoora.com/invoiceincoming/details/a81bc81b-dead-4e5d-abff-90865d1e13b1"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Invalid request payload.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Error"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Unauthorized request."
          }
        },
        "operationId": "postImport"
      },
